#: ../../../interop/vfio-user.rst:1776
msgid ""
"*page_size* hints what tracking granularity the device should try to "
"achieve. If the device cannot do the hinted page size then it's the driver's "
"choice which page size to pick based on its support. On output the device "
"will return the page size it selected."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../interop/vfio-user.rst:1781
msgid ""
"*num_ranges* is the number of IOVA ranges to monitor. A value of zero "
"indicates that all writes should be logged."
msgstr ""

