"Upon ``VFIO_DEVICE_FEATURE_GET``, returns the dirty bitmap for a specific "
"IOVA range. This operation is only valid if logging of dirty pages has been "
"previously started by setting ``VFIO_DEVICE_FEATURE_DMA_LOGGING_START``."
